==甲烷==
火星大氣可能含有 1nmol/mol 的甲烷。<ref name="methane">{{Cite web|title=Mars Express confirms methane in the Martian atmosphere|author=[[ESA|ESA]] Press release|publisher=[[ESA|ESA]]|url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Mars_Express/SEMZ0B57ESD_0.html|accessdate=March 17, 2006|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060224102528/http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Mars_Express/SEMZ0B57ESD_0.html|archivedate=2006年2月24日|deadurl=no}}</ref>


